'''Afurika Tshipembe''' (''Riphabuḽiki ya Afurika Tshipembe''; ''Republic of South Africa'') ndi shango li no wanala kha pida thsa tshipembe tsha dzhango la [[Afurika]]. Mashango are tsini nalo ndi [[Zimbagwe]], [[Namibia]], [[Mozambikwi]] (mozambique), [[Swazini]] (Swaziland), [[li-Sotho]] (Lesotho) na [[Vhu-Tswana]] (Botswana).

Afurika Tshipembe i na dzi phurovinsi dza tahe (9). Dzenedzo ndi [[Limpopo]], [[Mpumalanga]], [[Devhula-Vhukovhela]] (North West), [[Gauteng]], [[Free State]], [[Kwazulu-Naltal]], [[Kapa Vhubvaduvha]] (Eastern Cape), [[Kapa Vhukovela]] (Western Cape), [[Kapa Devhula]] (Northern Cape).

Afurika Tshipembe hu na nyambo dza fumi na nthihi dza tshiofhisi. Dzenedzo ndi [[TshiVenda]], [[English]], [[XiTsonga]], [[SiPedi]] (Northern Sotho, [[SeTswana]], [[SeSotho]], [[IsiZulu]], [[IsiNdebele]], [[IsiSwati]], [[IsiXhoza]]. Hu na dzinwe dzinyambo inzhi dzi si dza tshiofisi dzine dza ambiwa Afurika Tshipembe.

Afurika Tshipembe li na divhazwakale khulwane. 

Vhathu vha Afurika Tshipembe ndi vhathu vha u funa pfunzo. Hu na dzi univesithi dza fumbili-ina. Dzinwe dza hone ndi [[Univesithi ya Venda]], [[Univesithi ya Limpopo]], [[Univesithi ya Pretoria]], [[Univesithi ya Witwatersrand]] (Wits) na [[Univesithi ya Johannesburg]]. [[Univesithi dza Afurika Tshipembe]] dzi khou thusa kha u alusa ndivha ya vhathu vha Afurika Tshipembe. 

